STATE OF MADHYA PRADESH V. SHOBHARAM & ORS [1966] INSC 110 (22 April 1966)

 22/04/1966 
ACT:
 Madhyabharat Panchayat Act (58 of 1949), s. 63-If violates Art. 22 of the Constitution.
 Constitution of India, 1950, Art. 22(1)-Right of accused to be defended by counsel-If ensures in cases when accused cannot be sentenced to imprisonment.
 
